lead_paragraph: Sixth-ranked Maryland won the Big Ten regular season title Sunday, getting a career-high 29 points from Tierney Pfirman and 24 from Brionna Jones in a surprisingly lopsided 110-77 victory over Minnesota.

headline.print_headline: No. 6 Maryland Beats Minnesota 110-77 to Win Big Ten Title
